Rex Features8 Bella Hadid came in the same shade as the carpet The Mega Agency8 She was loving her scarlet gown at today's premiere ¬†Model Bella, 22, was among the first to arrive at today's premiere for Penelope Cruz movie Pain and Glory in a scarlet Grecian gown. ¬†Amber, 33, was close behind in an ruffled silk gown with leather thigh-high boots, waving to the crowds who were craning their necks for a glimpse of red-carpet glamour. ¬†Meanwhile the film's star Penelope, 45, wore a large blue and white lace gown, laughing with her co-star Antonio Banderas as they strolled in. ¬†The Mask of Zorro actor, 58, held hands with his banker girlfriend Nicole Kimpel, 38, as the pair made their way in to watch the movie. Reuters8 Amber Heard teamed her dress with thigh-high leather boots Reuters8 Penelope is starring in the movie Pain And Glory The Mega Agency8 Antonio Banderas and girlfriend Nicole Kimpel Rex Features8 Rita dazzled on the way to her evening do Rex Features8 Liam smouldered for the cameras tonight Getty - Contributor8 The pair posed together inside the bash ¬†And the glamour rolled on into the night too, with yet more stars pitching up at the super-luxe Hotel Du Cap-Eden-Roc this evening. ¬†Among them were Liam, 25, and Rita, 28, who arrived at the fancy party party - dubbed the 'Filmmakers Dinner' - separately. ¬†However, the pair, who worked together on Fifty Shades Freed, posed together inside and were seated on the same table at the dinner.  ¬†Got a story? email digishowbiz@the-sun.co.uk or call us direct on 02077824220. ¬†We pay for videos too.
